arStrings.szText: "What can you tell me of the Knights in Seven Stones?"
Nobody escapes the jungle unmarked by the Knights' violence. Missing limbs, removed skin, branding, all are too common.
They wield their damned faith like any blade, use it to justify their cruelty towards others. You ask me, theyâ€™re no better than Dregs.
You're not planning to confront them, are you?
